  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigation of wholebody MRI and circulating biomarkers of inflammation, cartilage and bone
      metabolism in patients with spondyloarthritis treated with adalimumab. Furthermore to compare
      ultrasound examination with wholebody MRI etc.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
