    <measure>Number of peripheral and axial joints and entheses with inflammation, circulating biomarkers of inflammation, cartilage and bone metabolism, conventional clinical parameters and changes in these during treatment with adalimumab.</measure>
    <time_frame>24 week</time_frame>
  </secondary_outcome>
